##---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------##
##
## Abstract:
##   Shell script emacs-nox: Start emacs-gtk in text-terminal mode.
## This shell script is intended to serve as an alternative the symbolic link /usr/bin/editor can refer to.
##
## Details:
##   None.
